      <div class="faq-item ">

        <h4 class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-primary">What is the purpose of the Online Recruitment System?</h4>

        <p>The Online Recruitment System is designed to streamline the hiring process by connecting job seekers with employers. It allows job seekers to create profiles, upload resumes, and apply for jobs, while employers can post job openings, review applications, and manage candidates efficiently.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h4 class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-primary">How do I apply for a vacancy?</h4>

        <p>To apply for a vacancy, find the job listing you are interested in and click the 'Apply' button. Fill out the application form and submit it.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">

        <h4 class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-primary">How do I register as a job seeker or employer?</h4>

        <p>To register, simply click on the “Register” button on the homepage. You’ll need to provide some basic information such as your name, email, password, and either your job seeker or employer details, depending on your choice. Once you submit your registration, your account will be activated.</p>

      </div>
       <div class="faq-item">

              <h4 class="list-group-item list-group-item-action list-group-item-primary">How do I apply for a job??</h4>

              <p>Once you find a job listing that interests you, click on the “Apply” button. You may need to upload your resume and cover letter if required. Ensure all your details are accurate before submitting your application. </p>

